# Docker Compose environment file (auto-loaded). Committed on purpose — it holds
# no secrets, only which server profiles start by default.
#
# Both game servers are gated by Compose profiles: `ffa` and `instagib` (plus
# `all`, which both belong to). COMPOSE_PROFILES sets what a plain
# `docker compose up -d` runs. Change it to `instagib` or `all` (comma-separated
# for several, e.g. `ffa,instagib`), or override per-command with a flag:
#   docker compose --profile all up -d
# A CLI --profile takes precedence over this value.
COMPOSE_PROFILES=ffa
